review_blob:
This is my favorite beer.   It has a consistent yeasty Belgian goodness, a nice warm afterglow thanks to its ABV. This beer has inspired me to search for other snazzy triples. Victory Golden Monkey comes close but New Belgium is the best. 

---Rated via Beer Buddy for iPhone

Ten Fidy. I'm a stout snob now. This is oil black perfection. How can this taste come out of a can?

---Rated via Beer Buddy for iPhone

Good brew for a blizzard night. Strong alcohol will chase any chill. The coffee cherries and a unique and exotic taste. I wish that they lingered longer.   A sipper beer that becomes more complex as it warms. 

---Rated via Beer Buddy for iPhone
beer_name: New Belgium Lips of Faith - Cascara Quad
